  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelStoryData
  levelName: 
  introLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "Cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng c\u0169ng t\u1EDBi n\u01A1i r\u1ED3i, th\u1EADt may
      tr\xEAn \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0111i c\u0169ng \xEDt g\u1EB7p b\u1ECDn ch\xFAng
      , hay c\xF3  g\xEC \u0111\xE3 thu h\xFAt ch\xFAng \u0111i nh\u1EC9 ?"
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "hahaha, Nh\u1ED9t  qu\xE1 Shadow tr\xE8o xu\u1ED1ng n\xE0o"
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "Ch\u1EDD  \u0111\xE3 Shadow , c\xF3 g\xEC \u0111ang ti\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EBFn
      k\xECa\u2026 , nh\xECn nh\u01B0 con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi sao \u2026? *nh\xECn r\xF5
      h\u01A1n khi ch\xFAng l\u1EA1i g\u1EA7n* c\u1EA9n th\u1EADn Shadow!!! Ch\xFAng
      kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE2u!!"
  outroLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "Chuy\u1EC7n qu\xE1i g\xEC \u0111ang x\u1EA3y ra \u1EDF n\u01A1i n\xE0y
      v\u1EADy??? ch\xE3 l\u1EBD slime \u0111\xE3 ti\u1EBFn h\xF3a v\xE0 \u0111\xE3
      c\xF3 th\u1EC3 chi\u1EBFm th\xE2n x\xE1c con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi r\u1ED3i sao ???
      C\xF3 v\u1EBB ch\xFAng ta ph\u1EA3i n\xEAn c\u1EA9n th\u1EADn h\u01A1n r\u1ED3i
      Shadow\u2026"
